###
# SPRINT 7: Self-Optimization - Ciclo Proativo de Auto-Melhoria
# Testes completos do ciclo MONITOR-DETECT-PLAN-EXECUTE-LEARN
###

@host = http://localhost:8000
@api_v1_prefix = /api/v1

###
# 1. Executar Ciclo Completo de Auto-Otimização
POST {{host}}{{api_v1_prefix}}/optimization/run-cycle
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enable_auto_execution": false
}

###
# 2. Executar Ciclo com Auto-Execução Habilitada
POST {{host}}{{api_v1_prefix}}/optimization/run-cycle
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enable_auto_execution": true,
  "max_improvements": 3
}

###
# 3. Obter Métricas de Saúde do Sistema
GET {{host}}{{api_v1_prefix}}/optimization/health
Accept: application/json

###
# 4. Listar Problemas Detectados
GET {{host}}{{api_v1_prefix}}/optimization/issues
Accept: application/json

###
# 5. Listar Problemas por Severidade (HIGH)
GET {{host}}{{api_v1_prefix}}/optimization/issues?severity=HIGH
Accept: application/json

###
# 6. Listar Problemas por Categoria (PERFORMANCE)
GET {{host}}{{api_v1_prefix}}/optimization/issues?category=PERFORMANCE
Accept: application/json

###
# 7. Obter Histórico de Métricas
GET {{host}}{{api_v1_prefix}}/optimization/metrics/history?limit=50
Accept: application/json

###
# 8. Obter Métricas de um Período Específico
GET {{host}}{{api_v1_prefix}}/optimization/metrics/history?start_time=2024-01-01T00:00:00&end_time=2024-12-31T23:59:59
Accept: application/json

###
# 9. Executar Análise de Performance
POST {{host}}{{api_v1_prefix}}/optimization/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "analysis_type": "performance",
  "detailed": true
}

###
# 10. Health Check do Sistema de Auto-Otimização
GET {{host}}{{api_v1_prefix}}/optimization/status
Accept: application/json
